nodes.text: A male smuggler worked as a black market merchant during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire, and sought help tracking down lost relics from a dig on the planet Dubrillion.

The smuggler was first mentioned in the Treasure Hunting Crew Skill Mission "Smuggler's Dig", in Star Wars Legends, a massively multiplayer online role-playing video game released by BioWare and LucasArts in 2011.
